data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Spring Branch, Texas! This charming single-story residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this meticulously maintained property is priced at $265,000, making it an ideal opportunity to embrace a serene and delightful lifestyle.    Nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this residence provides a tranquil retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. The well-designed layout features a seamless flow, showcasing a spacious living area, a fully-equipped kitchen, and three cozy bedrooms.    One of the standout features of this property is its prime location. Situated within walking distance to the Neighborhood Riverside Park, residents can enjoy the beauty of nature and engage in various outdoor activities. Additionally, the convenience of a nearby county boat ramp adds an extra layer of recreational opportunities, making this home a haven for nature enthusiasts and water lovers.    Whether you're relaxing in the comfort of your home or exploring the nearby park, this residence offers a perfect balance of serenity and accessibility. Don't miss the chance to make this tranquil oasis your own - a welcoming haven in the heart of Spring Branch, Texas.
